videos.description: St. John's LJ Figueroa lobs it high to Justin Simon who throws down a nice two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Simon throws down alley-oop slam

videos.description: Justin Simon comes up with a steal and rises for a nasty slam that extends St. John's lead over Marquette.
videos.headline: Simon skies emphatic slam

videos.description: Sacar Anim comes up big as he drills a contested 3-pointer to give Marquette the lead late.
videos.headline: Marquette's Anim drills go-ahead 3-pointer
